00042 function bytes_to_s ($bytes)
00043 {
00044   if (($bytes/1073741824) > 1 ) {
00045     return intval($bytes/1073741824). "G";
00046   } else if (($bytes/1048576) > 1) {
00047     return intval($bytes/1048576). "M";
00048   } else if (($bytes/1024) > 1) {
00049     return intval($bytes/1024). "K";
00050   } else {
00051     return $bytes;
00052   }
00053 }

00055 function parse_queue_data ($qdata)
00056 {
00057   $qdata = preg_replace ("/\n/", "", $qdata);
00058   foreach (preg_split("/queue/", $qdata, '-1', PREG_SPLIT_NO_EMPTY) as $qline) {
00059 
00060     /*
00061      * Sanitize the rule string so that we can deal with '{foo' as '{ foo' in 
00062      * the code further down without any special treatment
00063      */
00064     $qline = preg_replace("/{/", " { ",   $qline);
00065     $qline = preg_replace("/}/", " } ",   $qline);
00066     $qline = preg_replace("/\(/", " ( ",  $qline);
00067     $qline = preg_replace("/\)/", " ) ",  $qline);
00068     $qline = preg_replace("/,/", "",   $qline);
00069     $qline = preg_replace("/\"/", " \" ", $qline);
00070     $qline = trim($qline);
00071 
00072     $qs = array();
00073     foreach (preg_split("/[\s\t]+/", $qline) as $qstatement) {
00074       $qs[] = $qstatement;
00075     }
00076 
00077     $qad = array();
00078     $qad['name'] = $qs[0];
00079     for ($i = '1'; $i < count($qs); $i++) {
00080         switch ($qs[$i]) {
00081         case "bandwidth":
00082         case "priority":
00083           $qad[$qs[$i]] = $qs[++$i];
00084           break;
00085         case "cbq":
00086         case "priq":
00087         case "hsfs":
00088           $qad["type"] = $qs[$i];
00089           break;
00090         case "pkts:":
00091           $qad["packets"] = bytes_to_s($qs[++$i]);
00092           break;
00093         case "bytes:":
00094           $qad["bytes"] = bytes_to_s($qs[++$i]). "b";
00095           break;
00096         case "borrows:":
00097           $qad["borrows"] = bytes_to_s($qs[++$i]);
00098           break;
00099         case "suspends:":
00100           $qad["suspends"] = bytes_to_s($qs[++$i]);
00101           break;
00102         case "dropped":
00103           $i += 2;
00104           $qad["dropped_packets"] = bytes_to_s($qs[$i]);
00105           $i += 2;
00106           $qad["dropped_bytes"] = bytes_to_s($qs[$i]). "b";
00107           break;
00108         case "qlength:":
00109           $qad["queue_length"] = $qs[++$i]. $qs[++$i];
00110           break;
00111         case "{":
00112           while (preg_replace("/[\s,]+/", "", $qs[++$i]) != "}") {
00113               $qad['childqueues'][] = $qs[$i];
00114           }
00115           break;
00116       case "(":
00117         while (preg_replace("/[\s,]+/", "", $qs[++$i]) != ")") {
00118           $qad['options'][] = $qs[$i];
00119         }
00120         break;
00121       }
00122     }
00123 
00124     $qa[] = $qad;
00125   }
00126   return $qa;
00127 }
